WEBVTT

00:03:29.600 --> 00:03:32.280
meaning the grandparents cloud.

00:03:32.920 --> 00:03:34.456
People who have the time,

00:03:34.480 --> 00:03:38.440
love children and know the internet.

00:03:39.960 --> 00:03:43.096
They would go there
and interact with them.

00:03:43.120 --> 00:03:47.400
So we merged both the ideas
and created a concept.

00:03:48.640 --> 00:03:51.496
In 2013, I got a prize from TED,

00:03:51.520 --> 00:03:52.976
so with that prize money,

00:03:53.000 --> 00:03:56.696
I created a concept called
"School In The Cloud."

00:03:56.720 --> 00:03:59.936
It means a school in clouds.

00:03:59.960 --> 00:04:03.720
These days, schools keep
the internet away from children,